node.text: This is from a time when I used to wait, wait for something but doing nothing to make it happens. This is from when I used to immobilise myself. Now it’s time to go on, to look forward, to look and begin to see everything for real. This is the time to do and to create new memories, the time to stop living in a painful past and start to enjoy the present. Things may change sometimes and so I have to change, stop destroying myself for someone who doesn’t care or deserve it. Sometimes thoughts need to be written. This is just a stream of consciousness, today is just a Monday morning like another, but every single day wouldn’t be like another from now on and I’m not going to be sorry for what is in my heart now or never.
And the shape of things to come.
The more I think, the less I know.

Here with me. { breathe and leave the world outside } .
🖤 Ph. @io_me_e_la_frency
When she smiles. { about a beautiful heart and soul }
Take the moment and make it perfect.
It’s ok not to be ok.
